OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,FA Nepali climbing guide, who was
OL,7,Fassumed to have died on Mount Everest,
OL,8,Fhas been found crawling down to base
OL,9,Fcamp, a week after going missing.
OL,11,FThe news came after his family had
OL,12,Fbegun a second day of funeral rites,
OL,13,Fhaving lost hope that he would be
OL,14,Ffound alive.
OL,16,FDawa Sherpa was seen descending Mount
OL,17,FEverest on May 29, but failed to
OL,18,Freturn to base camp, despite his
OL,19,Fclient making it down safely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
