PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780653972
OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,FThe pair were among the final climbers
OL,7,Fon the mountain as the climbing season
OL,8,Fdrew to a close and routes were being
OL,9,Fdismantled.
OL,11,FThe 52-year-old was found alive on
OL,12,FThursday morning by a clean-up team,
OL,13,Fwho spotted him crawling down snowy
OL,14,Fslopes near the Khumbu Icefall above
OL,15,FBase Camp, according to Pemba Sherpa
OL,16,Fof 8K Expeditions, who coordinated the
OL,17,Fsearch.
OL,19,FHe was quickly carried down to safety
OL,20,Fand given food and water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
