PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780653972
OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,FA rescue helicopter flew him to HAMS
OL,7,FHospital in Kathmandu, where his wife
OL,8,Fand daughter, who had already begun
OL,9,Ffuneral rituals for him, were waiting.
OL,11,F"We first heard that he was still
OL,12,Falive on the local news and from a
OL,13,Fperson we know who called with the
OL,14,Fnews that... he is being brought
OL,15,Fdown," Damu Sherpa, his wife, said.
OL,17,FAlthough Dawa had been missing since
OL,18,Flast week, there was a delay in
OL,19,Forganising a search team.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780653972
OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,FNo reason has been given for the
OL,7,Fdelay, and when helicopters were
OL,8,Feventually deployed, they were unable
OL,9,Fto locate him.
OL,11,FHis family had already begun mourning
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,FDawa's teenage daughter, Mendo Lhamu
OL,15,FSherpa, said they were on the second
OL,16,Fday of funeral rites, having lost hope
OL,17,Fthat he would be found alive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780653972
OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,F"When we first heard about it (the
OL,7,Frescue), we could not be sure if that
OL,8,Fperson was indeed our father," Mendo
OL,9,FLhamu said.
OL,11,F"So, to be certain, we asked for
OL,12,Fphotos to be sent, and then only we
OL,13,Fwere sure and very happy."
OL,15,FThe team that found Dawa was part of
OL,16,Fthe Sagarmatha Pollution Control
OL,17,FCommittee, which installs ladders and
OL,18,Fropes along Everest routes at the
OL,19,Fstart of each climbing season, then
OL,20,Fremoves the equipment and clears
OL,21,Frubbish once climbers have left.
