PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780653972
OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,FDawa, who is from the town of
OL,7,FOkhaldhunga, south of Everest, was
OL,8,Flast seen near the Yellow Band above
OL,9,FCamp 3, at an altitude of around 7,200
OL,10,Fmetres. Everest Base Camp sits at
OL,11,Fabout 5,300 metres.
OL,13,FHe works for Himalayan Traverse and
OL,14,Fhad been guiding a Polish climber when
OL,15,Fhe went missing.
OL,17,FMembers of Nepal's Sherpa climbing
OL,18,Fcommunity have described his survival
OL,19,Fas miraculous.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
