PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780653972
OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,F"This is nothing short of a miracle
OL,7,Fsurviving so many days on the
OL,8,Fmountains facing such harsh
OL,9,Fcondition," Ang Tshering Sherpa, a
OL,10,Fleading figure in the community, said.
OL,12,F"Sherpas are built tough growing up in
OL,13,Fthe mountains," Ang Tshering said
OL,15,F"If there was someone else in his
OL,16,Fplace they might not have survived."
