OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,FMembers of the Sherpa community were
OL,7,Ftraditionally yak herders and traders
OL,8,Fliving in remote parts of the
OL,9,FHimalayas until Nepal opened its
OL,10,Fborders to foreigners in the 1950s.
OL,12,FTheir stamina and knowledge of the
OL,13,Fmountains soon made them highly sought-
OL,14,Fafter as guides and porters, helping
OL,15,Fthem become central figures in the
OL,16,FHimalayan climbing industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
