PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780653972
OL,3,CSherpa guide feared dead on Mount
OL,4,CEverest is found alive after six days
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 climbers and guides
OL,7,Freached the summit of Mount Everest
OL,8,Fthis May, making it the busiest
OL,9,Fclimbing season ever on the world's
OL,10,Fhighest peak.
OL,12,FThe season started later than usual
OL,13,Fafter a huge block of ice above Base
OL,14,FCamp took around two weeks to clear.
OL,16,FMount Everest was first climbed on 29
OL,17,FMay 1953 by Edmund Hillary and Tenzing
OL,18,FNorgay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
